{"tid":579132,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"apple向htc致敬，重新定義edge sense","createTime":"2018-03-03T10:16:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-04T13:51:43.000Z","uid":55951,"like":22,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"9656b887fc3f3c041e664c8af4f141dd90714866","tid":579132,"uid":55951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T10:16:57.000Z","msg":"據外媒 Patently Apple報導指出，從近日曝光的蘋果最新專利文件申請看來，似乎正朝向在 iPhone 機身側邊的邊框上，加入具備「觸控按鍵」的全新功能。<br />\n<br />\nPatently Apple 報導表示，有關這項按鍵設計的新專利，文件內容描述提到，透過機身側邊設置的虛擬按鍵或實體按鍵，具備有先進的觸控回饋技術新功能，將可感應用戶的指紋、與按壓力道，並可根據不同的按壓力道，啟動手機的應用功能，例如：啟動相機拍照等。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，蘋果早在2016年8年，就已正式取得有關機身螢幕側邊虛擬按鈕的專利。近日這份曝光的新文件，是在2017年第四季向美國專利商標局申請遞出申請，主要是延續先前專利在後續加入新技術功能方面的作業程序。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://3c.ltn.com.tw/m/news/33122\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F3c.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Fnews%2F33122&d=mNAIbFpH%2FXaHed9whc5ruTOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=4e9dd3ee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2F3c.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Fnews%2F33122&h=626bafa4\" target=\"_blank\">http://3c.ltn.com.tw/m/news/33122</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.patentlyapple.com/patently-apple/2018/02/apple-tweaks-iphone-with-sidewall-icons-invention-by-adding-force-touch-and-more.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.patentlyapple.com%2Fpatently-apple%2F2018%2F02%2Fapple-tweaks-iphone-with-sidewall-icons-invention-by-adding-force-touch-and-more.html&d=mNAIbFpH%2FXaHed9whc5ruTOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=806ace1e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.patentlyapple.com/patently-apple/2018/02/apple-tweaks-iphone-with-sidewall-icons-invention-by-adding-force-touch-and-more.html</a>"},{"pid":"fedab71f9c39c25c5e8cd86d7887404c36be6ecf","tid":579132,"uid":32577,"like":32,"dislike":3,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T10:21:43.000Z","msg":"apple同htc簽左互相授權專利喎"},{"pid":"f250e6c619ff197413f5e9694df5f62f7abff0cd","tid":579132,"uid":37688,"like":99,"dislike":4,"score":95,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T1